    "body": "##  Insight\nWhen using Qwen3-32B-FP8, the decode stage is using cutlass FP8, which makes it slower than sglang\n* vLLM 27ms \n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e5e63fde-71c5-4b14-b3e9-e607e4fec9a6)\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/81d2943c-37b1-4000-8920-3698d9c44434)\n\n* sglang 14ms\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/abfe852a-e31c-4e9b-ad1a-9526db46c347)\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b9f25d53-80ba-436a-9ee4-4a3a84a705f3)\n\nAnd as I checked, vLLM use DeepGEMM in MOE, but not in FP8LinearMethod\nSo I add an option to use DeepGEMM and JIT as sglang does\n\n## Accuracy Result\n* origin cutlass FP8 decode\n\n`VLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 lm_eval --model vllm --model_args pretrained=/mnt/Qwen3-32B-FP8 --tasks gsm8k --batch_size auto`\n\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.6224|±  |0.0134|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.7445|±  |0.0120|\n\n\n* our DeepGEMM FP8 decode\n\n`VLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=1 lm_eval --model vllm --model_args pretrained=/mnt/Qwen3-32B-FP8 --tasks gsm8k --batch_size auto`\n\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.6346|±  |0.0133|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.7430|±  |0.0120|\n\n\n\n\n## Performance Result\n\n\n* origin cutlass FP8 decode\n\n`VLLM_USE_V1=1 VLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 vllm serve Qwen/Qwen3-32B-FP8/  --no-enable-prefix-caching`\n\n```\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\nSuccessful requests:                     10\nBenchmark duration (s):                  4.56\nTotal input tokens:                      1000\nTotal generated tokens:                  1000\nRequest throughput (req/s):              2.19\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         219.24\nTotal Token throughput (tok/s):          438.48\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\nMean TTFT (ms):                          291.90\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        318.24\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           319.53\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\nMean TPOT (ms):                          43.06\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        42.83\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           44.89\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\nMean ITL (ms):                           43.06\nMedian ITL (ms):                         42.89\nP99 ITL (ms):                            43.39\n==================================================\n```\n* our DeepGEMM FP8 decode\n\n`VLLM_USE_V1=1 VLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=1 vllm serve Qwen/Qwen3-32B-FP8/  --no-enable-prefix-caching`\n\n```\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\nSuccessful requests:                     10\nBenchmark duration (s):                  2.51\nTotal input tokens:                      1000\nTotal generated tokens:                  1000\nRequest throughput (req/s):              3.98\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         398.03\nTotal Token throughput (tok/s):          796.07\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\nMean TTFT (ms):                          287.71\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        314.18\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           315.46\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\nMean TPOT (ms):                          22.43\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        22.18\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           24.44\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\nMean ITL (ms):                           22.43\nMedian ITL (ms):                         22.24\nP99 ITL (ms):                            22.69\n==================================================\n```\n\n* to reproduce\n```\npython3 benchmark_serving.py  --model /data/Qwen3-32B-FP8 --num-prompts 10 --dataset-name random --random-input-len 100 --random-output-len 100 --ignore-eos\n```\n\n* need to pre-install DeepGEMM\n```\ngit clone https://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepGEMM.git --recursive\ncd DeepGEMM && git checkout bfe983c\npython setup.py install\n```\n\n* support for vLLM V1 and torch.compile is done ",
